#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:27
msgid "Speech to text"
msgstr "Spraak naar tekst"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:33
msgid ""
"Speech to text doesn't work with version 21.04.2 due to `Vosk API <"
"https://"
"github.com/alphacep/vosk-api>`_ issues. Use version 21.04.1 or 21.04.3"
" and "
"later versions."
msgstr ""
"Spraak naar tekst werkt niet met versie 21.04.2 vanwege problemen met"
" `Vosk "
"API <https://github.com/alphacep/vosk-api>`_. Gebruik versie 21.04.1 of "
"21.04.3 en latere versies."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:37
msgid "Install Python"
msgstr "Python installeren"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:39
msgid ""
"Python 3 needs to be installed on your computer as well as the vosk and"
" srt "
"python modules:"
msgstr ""
"Python 3 moet geïnstalleerd zijn op uw computer evenals de python-modulen "
"vosk en srt:"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:42
msgid "Linux"
msgstr "Linux"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:44
msgid ""
"On most Linux distributions python is installed by default. You can check"
" if "
"that is the case for you too by running ``python3 -V`` in a terminal. If "
"python is missing just search the internet, there are lots of"
" instructions "
"around."
msgstr ""
"Op de meeste Linux distributies is python standaard geïnstalleerd. U kunt "
"controleren of dat voor u het geval is door ``python3 -V`` in een"
" terminal "
"uit te voeren. Als python ontbreekt zoek dan op het internet, er zijn"
" veel "
"instructies beschikbaar."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:46
msgid ""
"To install vosk and srt open a terminal and run: ``pip3 install vosk srt``"
msgstr ""
"om vosk en srt te installeren, open een terminal en voer uit: ``pip3"
" install "
"vosk pip3``"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:49
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Windows"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:51
msgid ""
"Download python from https://www.python.org/downloads/ for installation"
" on "
"your computer."
msgstr ""
"Download python vanaf https://www.python.org/downloads/ voor installatie"
" op "
"uw computer."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:52
msgid ""
"Download this batch file (:download:`Install_vosk_srt.zip </files/"
"Install_vosk_srt.zip>`). After download a double click starts the "
"installations."
msgstr ""
"Download dit batch-bestand (:download:`Install_vosk_srt.zip </files/"
"Install_vosk_srt.zip>`). Na downloaden start dubbelklikken de"
" installaties."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:57
msgid "Install a language"
msgstr "Een taal installeren"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:59
msgid ""
"Goto :menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Kdenlive... --> Speech to"
" Text "
"page`"
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Instellingen --> Kdenlive configureren... -->"
" Pagina "
"Spraak naar tekst`"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:61
msgid "Click on the link to get a language model."
msgstr "Klik op de koppeling om een taalmodel op te halen."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:66
msgid ""
"Drag & drop the language you want from the vosk-model download page to"
" the "
"model window, and it will download and extract it for you."
msgstr ""
"Sleep & laat de taal vallen die u wilt uit de downloadpagina van het vosk-"
"model naar het modelvenster en het zal voor u gedownload en uitgepakt"
" worden."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:71
msgid ""
"If you have problems press on the :guilabel:`Check configuration` button."
msgstr ""
"Als u problemen hebt druk op de knop :guilabel:`Configuratie controleren`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:74
msgid "Speech recognition"
msgstr "Spraakherkenning"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:77
msgid "Creating subtitle by speech recognition"
msgstr "Ondertiteling aanmaken door spraakherkenning"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:82
msgid ""
"Mark the timeline zone you want to recognize (adjust the blue line)."
msgstr ""
"Markeer de tijdlijnzone die u wilt herkennen (pas de blauwe lijn aan)."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:84
msgid "Click on the :guilabel:`Speech recognition` icon."
msgstr "Klik op het pictogram :guilabel:`Spraakherkenning`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:86
msgid "Choose the language."
msgstr "Kies de taal."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:88
msgid "Choose how the selected zone should be applied."
msgstr "Kies hoe de geselecteerde zone toegepast zou moeten worden."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:90
msgid "Press on the :guilabel:`Process` button."
msgstr "Druk op de knop :guilabel:`Proces`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:92
msgid "The subtitle gets created and inserted automatically."
msgstr "De ondertitel wordt aangemaakt en automatisch ingevoegd."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:94
msgid ""
"Remark: Only timeline zone is implemented for now in automatic subtitles."
msgstr ""
"Opmerking: alleen tijdlijnzone is voor nu geïmplementeerd in automatische "
"ondertitels."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:96
msgid ""
"Remark to 4: The default is to analyze only the :guilabel:`timeline zone "
"(all tracks)` (the blue bar in the timeline ruler). Set the zone in the "
"timeline to what you want to analyze (use :kbd:`I` and :kbd:`O` to set in "
"and out points). :guilabel:`Selected clips` option analyses the selected "
"clip only."
msgstr ""
"Opmerking bij 4: de standaard is om alleen de :guilabel:`tijdlijnzone "
"(alle tracks)` te analyseren (de blauwe balk in de tijdlijnliniaal). Stel "
"de zone in in de tijdlijn op wat u wilt analyseren (gebruik :kbd:`I` en "
":kbd:`O` om in- en uitpunten in te stellen). Optie :guilabel:"
"`Geselecteerde clips` analyseert alleen de geselecteerde clip."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:99
msgid "Creating clips by speech recognition"
msgstr "Clips aanmaken met spraakherkenning"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:101
msgid ""
"This is useful for interviews and other speech-related footage. Enable"
" the :"
"menuselection:`View --> Text Edit` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Dit is nuttig voor interviews en andere spraakgerelateerde opnamen."
" Schakel "
"het menu-item :menuselection:`Beeld --> Tekstbewerking` in."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:107
msgid "Select a clip in the project bin."
msgstr "Selecteer een clip in de project-bin."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:109
msgid ""
"If needed set in/out point in the clip monitor and enable :guilabel:"
"`Selected zone only` selection box. This will only recognize the text"
" inside "
"the zone."
msgstr ""
"Indien nodig stel in/uitpunt in in de clipmonitor en schakel keuzevak :"
"guilabel:`Alleen geselecteerde zone` in. Dit zal alleen de tekst in de"
" zone "
"herkennen."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:111
msgid "Choose the correct language."
msgstr "Kies de juiste taal."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:113
msgid "Press the :guilabel:`Start Recognition` button."
msgstr "Druk op de knop :guilabel:`Herkenning starten`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:115
msgid "Selecting the text you want to either."
msgstr "De tekst selecteren die u wilt invoeren."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:117
msgid "Put into the timeline."
msgstr "In de tijdlijn zetten."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:119
msgid ":guilabel:`Save` edited text as a new playlist."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opslaan` van bewerkte tekst als een nieuwe afspeellijst."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:121
msgid ""
"Add a Bookmark. You can jump to these bookmarks in the timeline with the :"
"kbd:`Alt + arrow` shortcut or edit the bookmark by double click."
msgstr ""
"Een bladwijzer toevoegen. U kun naar deze bladwijzers in de tijdlijn "
"springen met de sneltoets :kbd:`Alt + arrow` of de bladwijzer bewerken"
" met "
"dubbelklikken."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:123
msgid "Delete the selection."
msgstr "De selectie verwijderen."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:125
msgid "Here you can search in the text."
msgstr "Hier kunt u in de tekst zoeken."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:127
msgid "And navigate up or down in the text."
msgstr "En omhoog en omlaag navigeren in de tekst."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:132
msgid "Silence detection"
msgstr "Detectie van stilte"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:134
msgid ""
"Open the clip in the clip monitor and open the speech editor window (:"
"menuselection:`View --> Speech Editor`) ."
msgstr ""
"De clip openen in de clipmonitor en het spraakbewerkervenster openen "
"(:menuselection:`Beeld --> Spraakbewerker`) ."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:136
msgid ""
"Select your language or :ref:`install_language` and download the model"
" for "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer uw taal of :ref:`install_language` en download het model ervoor."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:138
msgid "Then click :guilabel:`Start Recognition` button."
msgstr "Klik daarna knop :guilabel:`Herkennen starten`."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:140
msgid ""
"Once this is done, click on the time-code where no-speech is indicated"
" and "
"just hit the :kbd:`delete` key. Repeat the operation for all the parts"
" you "
"want to remove, including where someone says what you don't want to"
" listen "
"in your final edit."
msgstr ""
"Nadat dit is gedaan, klik op de tijdcode waar geen spraak is aangegeven "
"en druk up de toets :kbd:`Delete`. Herhaal de bewerking voor alle delen "
"die u wilt verwijderen, inclusief waar iemand iets zegt wat u niet naar "
"wilt luisteren in uw uiteindelijke bewerking."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/speech_to_text.rst:142
msgid ""
"Once finished, make sure :guilabel:`Selected zone only` is disabled,"
" click "
"on the :guilabel:`Save` button on the lower left part of the speech"
" editor "
"window and after few seconds a new playlist is added in the project bin "
"without silence and without the text you don't want."
msgstr ""
"Nadat u klaar bent, ga na dat :guilabel:`Alleen geselecteerde zone` is "
"uitgeschakeld, klik op de knop :guilabel:`Opslaan` aan het linksonder "
"deel van het spraakbewerkervenster en na enkele seconden wordt een nieuwe "
"afspeellijst toegevoegd in de project-bin zonder stilte en zonder de "
"tekst die u niet wilt."
